def calculate_max_jokes(n, d, song_times):
    total_song_time = sum(song_times)
    total_rest_time = (n - 1) / 10
    total_time_required = total_song_time + total_rest_time
    if total_time_required > d:
        return -1
    remaining_time = d - total_time_required
    max_jokes = remaining_time // 5
    return max_jokes
